  • Type Parameters:
    S - a RadioSource type.
    public class RangingRadioSourceEstimator2D<S extends RadioSource>
extends RangingRadioSourceEstimator<S,​com.irurueta.geometry.Point2D>
    Estimates position of a radio source (e.g. WiFi access point or bluetooth beacon) by using ranging measurements. Ranging measurements can be obtained by protocols such as ieee 802.11mc (WiFi RTT) which measures travel time of signal and converts the result into distances by taking into account the speed of light as the propagation speed.
